text: Sherin Taama (, born May 26, 1982 in Alexandria) is an Egyptian rhythmic gymnast. Taama competed for Egypt in the rhythmic gymnastics individual all- around competition at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. She placed 24th in the qualification round and did not advance to the final. == References == == External links == * Sherin Taama at Sports-Reference.com Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian rhythmic gymnasts Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic gymnasts of Egypt Category:Sportspeople from Alexandria Category:Competitors at the 2001 World Games
